====================================================================
= Compatibilty step for version of bigloo < 3.4b                   =
====================================================================

If you run a version of bigloo < 3.4b then you first need to copy
Makefile.api into the default bigloo library directory, that you can
obtain using :

	* bigloo -q -eval "(begin (print *default-lib-dir*) (exit 0))"

====================================================================
= Default installation                                             =
====================================================================

To install camloo, untar the archive and do :

   * make
   * sudo make install
   * (you may then need to do 'sudo ldconfig')

====================================================================
= Testing your installation                                        =
====================================================================

You can the run the test suits by doing :

	* make tests

if you want to check that your installation is correct.